  <md:title>Collaborative Statistics Using Spreadsheets: Two column Step by Step form for Sampling Distribution and Confidence Intervals</md:title>
  <md:abstract>This is a two column step by step form for students to use to conduct a sampling distribution or a confidence interval for a sample of data.</md:abstract>
